{252}{}{你团结了部落，伟大的领袖。下一步该做什么由你决定。但如果你与游骑兵结盟，你就会让部落陷入无休止的战争。 -- You have united the tribe, great leader. It's up to you to decide what to do next. But by making an alliance with the Rangers, you doom the tribe to an endless war.}
