{253}{}{也许真相是你的。凤凰帝国强大而伟大。我们将无法抵抗，总有一天我们会放弃。如果我们加入帝国，我们将保持一定的独立性。 -- Perhaps the truth is yours. The Phoenix Empire is strong and great. We will not be able to resist and someday we will give up. If we join the empire, we will retain some independence.}
